did.head: Collection Summary

repository.corpname: Woodson Research Center, Rice University, Houston, Texas

did.unittitle: Rice University Association of Rice Alumni records
did.abstract: This collection contains records and items related to the Association of Rice Alumni. It includes records and meeting minutes of various alumni committees and boards.

bioghist.head: Historical Note
bioghist.p: "The purpose of the Association of Rice Alumni (ARA) is to provide the means of a continuing relationship between the university and its former students.

The association strives to stimulate intellectual and social participation of all members of the ARA, and to enable them to contribute to and share in the enhancement of the university. In addition, the association endeavors to foster deeper concern among its members for the welfare of the university, to strengthen the bond of understanding between the university and the community, to encourage gifts, to attract outstanding students and faculty, and to contribute toward maintaining Rice as a university in keeping with the ideals and aims of its founder.
The Association of Rice Alumni (ARA) is governed by the ARA Board in conjunction with the Office of Alumni Affairs."

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection contains records and items related to the Association of Rice Alumni. It includes records and meeting minutes of various alumni committees and boards.

accessrestrict.head: Access Restrictions
accessrestrict.p: This material is open for research, except where noted.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Stored offsite at the Library Service Center and require 24-hour notice for retrieval. Please contact the Woodson Research Center at 713-348-2586 or woodson@rice.edu for more information.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: The items in this collection were donated or transferred to Woodson Research Center at various times between 1980 and 2019. Additional accruals are expected.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Rice University Association of Rice Alumni records, 1922-2019, UA 003, Woodson Research Center, Fondren Library, Rice University.

separatedmaterial.head: Separated Materials
separatedmaterial.p: Sports and special event clothing items donated by Rice alumni have been removed from this collection and are now located in UA 392.

userestrict.head: Use Restrictions
userestrict.p: Permission to publish from this material must be obtained from Woodson Research Center, Fondren Library, Rice University.
